News.headline: BBC Essex Senior Cup Fourth Round Draw
News.page_title: BBC Essex Senior Cup Fourth Round Draw
News.URL_keywords: BBC Essex Senior Cup Fourth Round Draw
News.short_description: The Daggers have been drawn to play Heybridge Swifts at home in the Fourth Round of the Essex Senior Cup.
News.description:
After defeating Southend United 3-0 in the third round of the Essex Senior Cup, the Daggers will play Heybridge Swifts at home in the Fourth round of the BBC Essex Senior Cup.

Fixture to be played on or before the 10th December.

Ticket details will be released in due course.
